    "Madras et al.",
    "propose an adversarial training-based methodto address issues of fairness and bias in machine learning models [100].",
    "The discriminator predicts the sensitive attribute from the learned representation, while the generator produces a representation that is both predictive of the task and fair.",
    "Another approach is the \"jointly constrained Naive Bayes\", which restricts the classifier to use only a subset of features that are minimally correlated with the protected attribute [66].",
